{"title":"我是故乡人——一位归国台胞的心声","authors":["张莹"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":6,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是故乡人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——一位归国台胞的心声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张莹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久违了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你——收留过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我幼小足痕的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然也是冬日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那两行白杨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也已没了衣裳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可我依旧沿着你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指明的方位"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找寻那曾属于我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己编织的故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡　过去的家园只是在你面前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我才敢自谓为诞生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而那小屋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或许能记起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我儿时的话语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"至于屋前的古井"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水是咸味儿的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不会忘却"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有几次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我摇把橹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天也嚼过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那井沿儿的冰块儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"童年的印象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"容纳的是整个田园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"婆婆丁　小根蒜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羞涩的红高粱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是那样地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛满了我的记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颔首略过双足"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却没了祖母的手艺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可皮鞋的底面也算"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带回了我的相思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几粒故土的分子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛为了示意我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要常吸吮一下那气息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再望望小路吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我走过的　依旧这等绵长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从心的一隅驶向天的一端"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于不曾计算出那极限"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可到任何时令"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我都能望到　望到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并这样沉吟　久违了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只为了能有今天"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}